CLIFF LUNGARETTI: Who has
the most impressive mustache,

00:35:58.155 --> 00:36:00.856
of all the guys that you've
met in your journey now?

00:36:00.856 --> 00:36:05.570
ADAM GARONE: Oh
I'd have to say--

00:36:05.570 --> 00:36:06.480
AUDIENCE: Right here.

00:36:07.757 --> 00:36:09.340
ADAM GARONE: That's
a ginger mustache.

